02:02.586 --> 02:05.998
Sir, can I partner with
Pimento on my B&E?

02:05.999 --> 02:07.066
That guy is awesome.

02:07.134 --> 02:08.701
He's like a real life
Donnie Brasco.

02:08.702 --> 02:11.668
Isn't Donnie Brasco a really
sad movie that ends terribly?

02:11.705 --> 02:12.972
Yeah, but he's got
that cool jacket,

02:12.973 --> 02:14.340
and he's always
down at the docks.

02:14.341 --> 02:15.808
