a very difficult transition.

02:23.417 --> 02:24.951
Yeah, I know, I went undercover.

02:24.952 --> 02:26.953
63 days, no big deal.
You probably forgot.

02:26.954 --> 02:28.685
No, it's your outgoing
voice mail message.

02:28.722 --> 02:29.722
<i>Hey, it's Jake.</i>

02:29.790 --> 02:31.190
Can't get to the phone
right now.

02:31.191 --> 02:34.393
I might be undercover again,
like I was for 63 days.

02:34.394 --> 02:35.561
Bye!

02:35.629 --> 02:37.930
Look, I know what
he's going through.

02:37.931 --> 02:40.132
Let me be the man
that brings him in from the cold.

02:40.133 --> 02:42.068
All right, he can work
the B&E with you.

02:42.069 --> 02:43.970
Just make sure you take it easy.

02:43.971 --> 02:46.505
Uh, sir, I was 20 minutes late
for work today.

02:46.506 --> 02:48.774
I don't think you need to
tell me about taking it easy.

02:48.775 --> 02:51.010
Are you bragging
about being a bad employee?

02:52.779 --> 02:54.714
No.

02:54.715 --> 02:56.349
Dismissed? Me?

02:56.416 --> 02:58.551
I figured out the best way

02:58.552 --> 03:00.586
to welcome Pimento
to the Nine-Nine.

03:00.587 --> 03:03.189
Stay out of his way,
maybe buy him a drink,

03:03.190 --> 03:04.624
not do anything weird?

03:04.691 --> 03:06.259
I'm making him a goat stew.

03:06.326 --> 03:08.183
Huh... all right.

03:08.228 --> 03:11.097
Yeah, now,
this Turkmenistani dish

03:11.098 --> 03:14.367
is traditionally made from
an animal that's been so overfed

03:14.368 --> 03:15.941
it can no longer stand.

03:16.003 --> 03:17.536
That's the dream.

03:17.537 --> 03:18.938
Everything is authentic.

03:18.939 --> 03:20.840
I even ordered
the pressure cooker

03:20.841 --> 03:22.008
from Turkmenistan.

03:22.075 --> 03:23.376
So you're on a terrorist
watch list now?

03:23.377 --> 03:25.845
Oh, yeah, Homeland Security's
been in my house, yep.

03:25.846 --> 03:29.215
Now, this just needs to cook for
another 11 hours, 32 minutes,

03:29.216 --> 03:31.817
and 6...

03:33.186 --> 03:36.455
What the hell, Boyle!
You almost killed me!

03:36.523 --> 03:38.758
I'm not going out
in a stew-making accident!

03:38.825 --> 03:40.993
Terry's gonna die
saving the President,

03:40.994 --> 03:43.062
or Terry's never gonna die!

03:43.063 --> 03:45.798
