clean this up by ourselves.

03:45.799 --> 03:47.166
We're gonna need help.

03:47.167 --> 03:48.701
No, no, no, no, no, no, no.

03:48.702 --> 03:49.702
What are you saying?

03:49.770 --> 03:52.038
You know what she's saying, man.

03:52.039 --> 03:54.006
Oh, no.

03:54.007 --> 03:55.474
Mean Marge.

03:55.542 --> 03:57.710
So we're supposed to come
running to clean up your mess

03:57.711 --> 03:59.912
every time you snap
your fat little fingers?

03:59.980 --> 04:01.447
Oh, no, no, I actually
can't snap my fingers,

04:01.448 --> 04:02.581
they're always too wet.

04:02.582 --> 04:04.150
And I just thought,
since it's your job...

04:04.151 --> 04:05.718
Oh, I see.

04:05.719 --> 04:08.387
You cops think you're too good
to clean up after yourselves?

04:08.388 --> 04:10.289
Uh... no, I can do it myself,
I'll just...

04:10.290 --> 04:11.657
That's union work!

04:11.725 --> 04:14.827
How dare you try
to steal our jobs.

04:14.828 --> 04:16.762
So where do we go from here?

04:16.829 --> 04:18.798
Well, you know the old saying,

04:18.798 --> 04:22.134
"The only way to unclog a toilet
is to let it sit."

04:22.135 --> 04:24.103
You're a janitor.
You should know that's not true.

04:24.171 --> 04:26.005
Boys, take out the trash.

04:26.073 --> 04:27.707
Oh, great!
So you will do it?

04:27.774 --> 04:29.075
Oh!
I'm the trash, I get it.

04:29.076 --> 04:30.676
Okay, that makes more sense
with your tone.

04:31.678 --> 04:34.013
Oops! Oh...
Love you, Marge.

04:34.014 --> 04:35.881
You wanted to see me, sir?

04:35.949 --> 04:37.750
Yes, I have a special
project for you.

04:37.751 --> 04:39.151
Okay, but I'll have
you know right now

04:39.152 --> 04:40.776
I only fly first class.

04:40.821 --> 04:42.254
I'm not flying you anywhere.

04:42.255 --> 04:44.657
I made an application to
the M.C. Guffin Foundation

04:44.658 --> 04:46.559
for a grant to upgrade
our office equipment.

04:46.560 --> 04:49.395
Unfortunately, they require
a video submission.

04:49.396 --> 04:51.364
I understand you have
some filmmaking experience.

04:51.431 --> 04:54.066
Well, you know, I've been
re-Vined by Rob Kardashian,

04:54.067 --> 04:56.001
so, yeah, I'm a director.

04:56.002 --> 04:57.203
Here's what I'm picturing:

04:57.204 --> 05:00.373
I enter, in, like,
a Fellini-style getup.

05:00.374 --> 05:02.141
Rosa's dressed
like a porcupine...

05:02.142 --> 05:03.909
Oh, no, no.
We're just gonna do a simple,

05:03.910 --> 05:05.778
straightforward tour
of the precinct

05:05.779 --> 05:07.213
featuring Detective Diaz and me.

05:07.280 --> 05:08.447
Are you sure?

05:08.448 --> 05:11.817
You're not our most dynamic
screen presences.

05:11.818 --> 05:12.985
I can be dynamic.

05:12.986 --> 05:14.387
Exclamation point.

05:14.388 --> 05:16.722
Well, Diaz and I have
that kind of easy chemistry

05:16.723 --> 05:18.591
- where we finish each other's...
- Sentences.

05:18.592 --> 05:20.626
Please, don't interrupt me.

05:20.627 --> 05:23.662
That kind of nonsense
won't happen on camera.

05:23.663 --> 05:25.264
Hey, hey, Pimento.

05:25.265 --> 05:26.265
Hey!

05:26.266 --> 05:28.033
This is my desk, okay?

05:28.034 --> 05:30.903
Okay, well,
now that that's out of the way,

05:30.971 --> 05:33.072
I was just coming to let you
know we're gonna work

05:33.073 --> 05:35.274
a B&E together;
we're gonna be partners.

05:35.275 --> 05:37.209
Nope.
I work alone.

05:37.210 --> 05:39.378
Plus, The Butcher says
he has spies in the NYPD,

05:39.379 --> 05:41.614
so I trust none of these dildos.

05:41.615 --> 05:43.482
Listen, you can trust me.

05:43.483 --> 05:45.484
- I'm, like, obsessed with you.
- Fine.

05:45.552 --> 05:48.421
Tell me something you've never
told another living soul.

05:48.422 --> 05:49.688
Um...

05:49.689 --> 05:51.056
Ooh, here's one.

05:51.057 --> 05:53.893
I'm actually not strong enough
to lift a water cooler jug,

05:53.894 --> 05:55.394
so I always find a way
to make Terry do it.

05:55.395 --> 05:56.762
Here's mine.

05:56.763 --> 05:58.297
Jimmy "The Butcher" made me
drive a croquet wicket

05:58.298 --> 06:01.333
through a guy's eyes
into his brain.

06:01.334 --> 06:04.570
Brain leaked out his eyes
like he was crying his own mind.

06:04.571 --> 06:06.205
My goodness.

06:06.206 --> 06:07.606
Now that I've heard yours,

06:07.607 --> 06:09.442
I feel like
my water cooler thing

06:09.443 --> 06:10.943
could have been
a little more juicy, but...

06:10.944 --> 06:13.679
No. That was
embarrassing for you.

06:13.680 --> 06:14.980
A bond has been made.

06:16.798 --> 06:18.617
Feels good to trust again,
brother.

06:18.618 --> 06:20.586
Wow, either you are a cyborg

06:20.587 --> 06:23.556
or you're carrying
so many weapons in this jacket.

06:23.557 --> 06:26.025
Hey.
Kitchen, now.

06:26.026 --> 06:27.126
Okay.

06:27.127 --> 06:28.327
What's up?

06:28.328 --> 06:29.895
Something's not right
about that guy.

06:29.896 --> 06:31.764
Why, just because he keeps
threatening to kill me

06:31.765 --> 06:33.899
in the middle of a police
precinct? Uh, grow up.

06:33.967 --> 06:35.301
Because I'm physically
attracted to him.

06:35.368 --> 06:36.869
And that's bad?

06:36.937 --> 06:39.004
the Vulture, the ShamWow guy,

06:39.005 --> 06:40.372
and when I was a kid,

06:40.373 --> 06:41.974
I had a major crush
on the evil Gremlin.

06:41.975 --> 06:43.676
Stripe?
Are you crazy?

06:43.743 --> 06:45.144
Yeah, well I'm not
gonna bone Gizmo.

06:45.145 --> 06:47.146
- I would.
- Careful with Pimento.

06:48.315 --> 06:49.615
It's gonna be fine.

06:53.334 --> 06:54.386
Hey, partner.

06:54.454 --> 06:56.453
- Oh!
- I've been waiting for you.

06:58.034 --> 06:59.596
Sorry if I surprised you.

06:59.597 --> 07:00.995
It's just when I was undercover,
the middle of the night

07:00.996 --> 07:03.109
was the only time
I could do actual police work.

07:03.110 --> 07:05.306
Uh, how'd you get
in the apartment?

07:05.307 --> 07:06.574
Oh, it was easy.

07:06.575 --> 07:08.108
I just seduced
the old lady upstairs,

07:08.109 --> 07:10.945
came down the fire escape,
jimmied the window open.

07:10.946 --> 07:13.547
Bing-bang-boom, I'm inside
your living quarters.

07:13.615 --> 07:15.082
Totally.

07:15.083 --> 07:17.651
Course, next time you could just
give me a call, you know.

07:17.652 --> 07:19.086
Two ways to pop in on a friend.

07:19.087 --> 07:20.254
I didn't kill
the old lady upstairs,

07:20.255 --> 07:21.422
if that's what
you're worried about.

07:21.489 --> 07:22.790
Well, I am now.

07:22.791 --> 07:24.124
Oh, wait a minute.

07:24.125 --> 07:26.093
You think I'm being weird.

07:26.094 --> 07:28.262
Oh, I shouldn't have come here.
This is your apartment.

07:28.263 --> 07:32.199
I'm so sorry, Jake!
Stupid, Paul!

07:32.200 --> 07:33.934
Stupid!
You idiot, Paul!

07:33.935 --> 07:35.469
- Hey! Pimento!
- Huh?!

07:35.537 --> 07:37.871
- Who's Paul?
- Whoa.

07:37.872 --> 07:39.573
Paul Sneed
was my undercover name.

07:39.574 --> 07:41.075
'Kay?
Damn it, Jake.

07:41.076 --> 07:42.457
I don't know who I am anymore.

07:42.510 --> 07:44.111
You could have chose
any name to go undercover,

07:44.112 --> 07:45.112
and you picked Paul Sneed?

07:45.113 --> 07:46.113
Seems kind of crazy.

07:46.114 --> 07:47.214
I shouldn't have come here.

07:47.215 --> 07:48.682
This was a mistake.
I'm not ready.

07:48.683 --> 07:51.085
I knew I wasn't ready
to go back to being police.

07:51.086 --> 07:53.287
It's the only job I've ever had
except for bagging groceries

07:53.288 --> 07:55.990
at the supermarket at the corner
of Atlantic and Clinton.

07:55.991 --> 07:58.025
I guess I could go back
to that again.

07:58.026 --> 07:59.460
"Paper or plastic?"

07:59.461 --> 08:00.861
Yeah, still got it.

08:00.862 --> 08:02.730
Listen to me, I was undercover.

08:02.731 --> 08:06.367
63 days with the Mafia.
I saw some messed-up stuff.

08:06.368 --> 08:08.369
I know what your struggle is.

08:08.370 --> 08:12.339
And I can bring you home,
but you've got to trust me.

08:12.340 --> 08:14.742
Okay. Yeah.

08:14.809 --> 08:17.444
Great. Now, I've got
to get some sleep.

08:17.445 --> 08:19.913
You're welcome to stay here
and work the case if you want.

08:19.914 --> 08:20.948
Thanks, partner.

08:20.949 --> 08:23.584
I promise I won't
disturb you at all.

08:24.653 --> 08:27.721
Whuuuhhhh.

08:27.789 --> 08:30.824
Whuuuhhhh.

08:30.825 --> 08:32.359
- Hey, Pimento.
- Huh?

08:32.427 --> 08:34.260
